accessibility.text: Educational goals inhere with the game goals, i.e.\u2028winning the game = achieving learning outcomes (LOs)\u2028\u2028\u2028
Drives struggling students to innovate new strategies for their learning\u2028
Cultivates intrinsic motivation (interest in the subject) among students that lasts\u2028after class, i.e. Life-long Learning\u2028\u2028
Greater knowledge retention, i.e. information sticks\u2028\u2028\u2028
Game storyline interconnects topics, i.e.\u2028say goodbye to Table of Contents\u2028\u2028\u2028\u2028
